remark">后台列表数目</p></td></tr><tr><td><input type="text" name="conf[LIST_GRID_NUMBER]" class="t_input w280" value="<?php echo ($conf["LIST_GRID_NUMBER"]); ?>" /><p class="remark">橱窗式列表数目</p></td></tr><tr><td><input type="text" name="conf[LIST_VIEW_NUMBER]" class="t_input w280" value="<?php echo ($conf["LIST_VIEW_NUMBER"]); ?>" /><p class="remark">普通列表数目</p></td></tr><tr><td>默认日期时间格式 &nbsp; : &nbsp; 
									<lable class="option_lable"><input type="radio" name="conf[DEFAULT_DATE_FORMAT]" value="Y-m-d"<?php if( $conf['DEFAULT_DATE_FORMAT'] == 'Y-m-d' ){ ?> checked="checked"<?php } ?> /><?php echo date('Y-m-d',time()); ?></lable><lable class="option_lable"><input type="radio" name="conf[DEFAULT_DATE_FORMAT]" value="m/d/Y"<?php if( $conf['DEFAULT_DATE_FORMAT'] == 'm/d/Y' ){ ?> checked="checked"<?php } ?> /><?php echo date('m/d/Y',time()); ?></lable><lable class="option_lable"><input type="radio" name="conf[DEFAULT_DATE_FORMAT]" value="Y年m月d日"<?php if( $conf['DEFAULT_DATE_FORMAT'] == 'Y年m月d日' ){ ?> checked="checked"<?php } ?> /><?php echo date('Y年m月d日',time()); ?></lable><lable class="option_lable"><input type="radio" name="conf[DEFAULT_DATE_FORMAT]" value="Y-m-d H:i:s"<?php if( $conf['DEFAULT_DATE_FORMAT'] == 'Y-m-d H:i:s' ){ ?> checked="checked"<?php } ?> /><?php echo date('Y-m-d H:i:s',time()); ?></lable><lable class="option_lable"><input type="radio" name="conf[DEFAULT_DATE_FORMAT]" value="m-d"<?php if( $conf['DEFAULT_DATE_FORMAT'] == 'm-d' ){ ?> checked="checked"<?php } ?> /><?php echo date('m-d',time()); ?></lable><lable class="option_lable"><input type="radio" name="conf[DEFAULT_DATE_FORMAT]" value="M d"<?php if( $conf['DEFAULT_DATE_FORMAT'] == 'M d' ){ ?> checked="checked"<?php } ?> /><?php echo date('M d',time()); ?></lable></td></tr><tr><td><textarea name="conf[SITE_DESCRIPTION]" class="t_input" style="width:560px; height:100px;"><?php echo ($conf["SITE_DESCRIPTION"]); ?></textarea><p class="remark">站点说明，SEO meta 相关，对网页的介绍，这些信息可能会出现在搜索结果中，因此需要根据网页的实际情况来设计，一般不超过200个字符。</p></td></tr><tr><td><textarea name="conf[SITE_FOOTER]" class="t_input" style="width:560px; height:100px;"><?php echo ($conf["SITE_FOOTER"]); ?></textarea><p class="remark">站点底部信息</p></td></tr><tr><td><input type="submit" value="提交修改" class="submit" /></td></tr></table></form></div><div class="nbox" id="wrap_system"><form action="<?php echo U('updateSettings');?>" method="post"><table class="table_form" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%"><tr><td><ol class="lists"><li><input type="radio" value="1" name="conf[CUSTOM_URL_MODEL]"<?php if( $conf['CUSTOM_URL_MODEL'] == 1 ){ ?> checked="checked"<?php } ?> /> 一般伪静态，如：http://<?php echo ($_SERVER['HTTP_HOST']); ?>/index.php/module<?php echo C('CUSTOM_URL_DEPR');?>action<?php echo C('CUSTOM_URL_DEPR');?>id<?php echo C('CUSTOM_URL_DEPR');?>1</li><li><input type="radio" value="2" name="conf[CUSTOM_URL_MODEL]"<?php if( $conf['CUSTOM_URL_MODEL'] == 2 ){ ?> checked="checked"<?php } ?> /> URL重写，需开启 URL_REWRITE 模式，必须支持“.htaccess”。如：http://<?php echo ($_SERVER['HTTP_HOST']); ?>/module<?php echo C('CUSTOM_URL_DEPR');?>action<?php echo C('CUSTOM_URL_DEPR');?>id<?php echo C('CUSTOM_URL_DEPR');?>1<?php echo C('CUSTOM_URL_SUFFIX');?></li><li><input type="radio" value="3" name="conf[CUSTOM_URL_MODEL]"<?php if( $conf['CUSTOM_URL_MODEL'] == 3 ){ ?> checked="checked"<?php } ?> /> 兼容模式，如：http://<?php echo ($_SERVER['HTTP_HOST']); ?>/?s=module<?php echo C('CUSTOM_URL_DEPR');?>action<?php echo C('CUSTOM_URL_DEPR');?>id<?php echo C('CUSTOM_URL_DEPR');?>1</li></ol></td></tr><tr><td><input type="text" name="conf[CUSTOM_URL_SUFFIX]" class="t_input w280" value="<?php echo ($conf["CUSTOM_URL_SUFFIX"]); ?>" /><p class="remark">URL 后缀名</p></td></tr><tr><td><input type="text" name="conf[CUSTOM_URL_DEPR]" class="t_input w280" value="<?php echo ($conf["CUSTOM_URL_DEPR"]); ?>" /><p class="remark">URL 参数分割符</p></td></tr><tr><td><input type="text" name="conf[THEME_LIST]" class="t_input w280" value="<?php echo ($conf["THEME_LIST"]); ?>" /><p class="remark">允许切换的主题，以英文逗号分割。</p></td></tr><tr><td><input type="submit" value="提交修改" class="submit" /></td></tr></table></form><br /><p class="upedwrap">URL 重写规则参考</p><div class="mt5" style="margin-left:10px;"><p class="mt5">Apache</p><p class="mt5"><code>
								&lt;IfModule mod_rewrite.c&gt;<br />
								RewriteEngine on<br />
								RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d<br />
								RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f<br />
								RewriteRule ^(.*)$ index.php/$1 [QSA,PT,L]<br />
								&lt;/IfModule&gt;
							</code></p><br /><hr /><br /><p class="mt5">IIS</p><p class="mt5"><code>RewriteRule (.*)$ /index\.php\?s=$1 [I]</code></p><br /><hr /><br /><p class="mt5">高版本IIS</p><p class="mt5"><code>
									&lt;rewrite&gt;<br />
									&lt;rules&gt;<br />
									&lt;rule name=&quot;OrgPage&quot; stopProcessing=&quot;true&quot;&gt;<br />
									&lt;match url=&quot;^(.*)$&quot; /&gt;<br />
									&lt;conditions logicalGrouping=&quot;MatchAll&quot;&gt;<br />
									&lt;add input=&quot;{HTTP_HOST}&quot; pattern=&quot;^(.*)$&quot; /&gt;<br />
									&lt;add input=&quot;{REQUEST_FILENAME}&quot; matchType=&quot;IsFile&quot; negate=&quot;true&quot; /&gt;<br />
									&lt;add input=&quot;{REQUEST_FILENAME}&quot; matchType=&quot;IsDirectory&quot; negate=&quot;true&quot; /&gt;<br />
									&lt;/conditions&gt;<br />
									&lt;action type=&quot;Rewrite&quot; url=&quot;index.php/{R:1}&quot; /&gt;<br />
									&lt;/rule&gt;<br />
									&lt;/rules&gt;<br />
									&lt;/rewrite&gt;
								</code></p><br /><hr /><br /><p class="mt5">Nginx</p><p class="mt5"><code>
									location / { <br />
										&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if (!-e $request_filename) {<br />
											&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;rewrite  ^(.*)$  /index.php?s=$1  last;<br />
											&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;break;<br />
										&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br />
									}
								</code></p></div></div><div class="nbox" id="wrap_attach">
